  "title": "Project Engineer",
  "description": "<p>The Role:</p><p>The candidate will coordinate project elements, and oversee the Project Team, and contractors to ensure that engineering projects are completed according to project plans and schedules, meet quality objectives, and comply with safety standards.</p><p><br /></p><p>Job Description</p><ul><li>Study on contract requirements, planning, and execution of project schedules.</li><li>Liaison and supervision of subcontractors for site progress installation.</li><li>Coordinates with vendors, subcontractors, and customers on project requirements, etc.</li><li>Site preparation and worker control for daily work and projects.</li><li>Prepare routine reports, service reports, and incident reports.</li><li>Other ad-hoc duties when assigned.</li></ul><p>Job Requirements</p><ul><li>Diploma of Electrical Engineering / Bachelor of Engineering in Civil Engineering</li><li>Preferably 0-2 years of relevant experience</li><li>Good interpersonal and communication skills.</li><li>Willing to hands-on, work irregular hours.</li><li>Able to work independently with minimal supervision.</li><li>Able to response to emergency call, if happens.</li><li>Preferably have a valid driving license and with own transport.</li></ul>",
